snippet: Stacy Lewis shot a seven-under-par 64 on Sunday to win the North Texas L.P.G.A. Shootout in Irving, finally getting another victory after six runner-up finishes in her previous 16 tournaments.
abstract: Stacy Lewis wins North Texas LPGA Shootout in Irving, Tex; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Stacy Lewis shot a seven-under-par 64 on Sunday to win the North Texas L.P.G.A. Shootout in Irving, finally getting another victory after six runner-up finishes in her previous 16 tournaments.
